BusTrInvolveInterestedPrsnGrp.TransactionDesc: THE ORGANIZATION ENTERED INTO A LEASE FOR A MEDICAL CLINIC WITH P.V. COMMUNITY DEVELOPMENT CORPORATION. ADDITIONALLY, PROJECT VIDA HEALTH CENTER AND P.V. COMMUNITY DEVELOPMENT CORPORATION OPERATE FROM THE SAME PRINCIPAL OFFICE.

PROJECT VIDA PROVIDES ADMINISTRATIVE SERVICES AND SERVES AS THE FISCAL AGENT FOR SEVERAL FUNCTIONS THAT OVERLAP WITH PROJECT VIDA HEALTH CENTER. PROJECT VIDA AND PVHC HAVE AN EMPLOYEE SHARING AGREEMENT THAT HAS BEEN EFFECTIVE SINCE 2017. PROJECT VIDA HEALTH CENTER ENTERED INTO A LEASE AGREEMENT FOR MEDICAL AND DENTAL CLINICS WITH PROJECT VIDA. ADDITIONALLY, BOTH ENTITIES HAVE AN INTER-AGENCY CASH FLOW LOAN AGREEMENT WHEREBY EACH ENTITY MAY BORROW FROM OR LEND TO THE OTHER FOR PURPOSES OF MEETING SHORT-TERM OBLIGATIONS. ALSO, PROJECT VIDA HEALTH CENTER CONTRACTED PROJECT VIDA TO PROVIDE ADMINISTRATIVE SUPPORT IN WHICH PROJECT VIDA ADVANCES PROJECT VIDA HEALTH CENTER OPERATION EXPENSES AND CHARGES PROJECT VIDA HEALTH CENTER FOR REIMBURSEMENT ON A MONTHLY BASIS. FOR THE YEAR ENDED AUGUST 31, 2022, PROJECT VIDA HEALTH CENTER OWED $181,395 TO PROJECT VIDA FOR SUCH EXPENSES.
